Gruta README
============

About
-----

Gruta is a web content management system written in Perl. Its goal is
to be a full featured CMS while having very few external dependencies. No
database is required (though you can use one).

Gruta powers the sites http://nutriguia.com and http://calendario-lunar.com
from year 2001, so its reliability is assured.

Installation
------------

